elements.name: Verify successful login with valid credentials

steps.name: the user is on the login page
the user logs in with valid credentials
the user should be redirected to the products page

elements.name: Validate error messages for invalid credentials and locked-out user

steps.name: the user is on the login page
the user logs in with invalid credentials
the user should see an invalid credentials error message
the user logs in with a locked-out account
the user should see a locked-out error message

elements.name: Add and remove multiple products from cart

steps.name: the user is logged in
the user adds multiple products to the cart
the user removes some products from the cart
the cart should display the correct product count and total amount
the user is on the products page
the user sorts products by name A to Z
the products should be displayed in alphabetical order
the user sorts products by price low to high
the products should be displayed in ascending price order
the user has products in the cart
the user proceeds to checkout
fills all required details
completes the order
the user should see a successful order confirmation message

elements.name: Validate negative and edge cases in checkout

embeddings.name: Validate negative and edge cases in checkout

steps.name: the user has products in the cart
the user proceeds to checkout without filling required fields
an error message should be displayed
the user accesses the cart without logging in
